## Data

The data used in this project were collected as part of an 8-day daily diary study conducted with undergraduate students at Brooklyn College (CUNY).

Participants completed daily surveys assessing climate-related emotions, climate conversations, and pro-environmental behaviors.

The dataset was originally collected using Qualtrics and exported in SPSS (.sav) format. Data were subsequently processed and analyzed in R.

Due to IRB restrictions, participant confidentiality, and consent procedures, the dataset is not publicly available and cannot be shared in this repository.

Researchers interested in accessing the data or learning more about the dataset may contact the Principal Investigator,  
Dr. Cheryl L. Carmichael, regarding potential access.
